Package: ASMK
Title: Accelerated Spatial Meta-Kriging (ASMK)
Version: 0.0-1
Authors@R: 
    person("Luca", "Presicce", , "l.presicce@campus.unimib.it", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-7062-3523"))
Description: "This package provides the computational framework to fit the Accelerated Spatial Meta-Kriging (ASMK) approach presented and detailed in Bayesian Transfer Learning and Divide-Conquer Models for Massive Spatial Datasets of Presicce L., and Banerjee S. (2024) <doi:10.48550/arXiv.0000.0000>. The functions in the package use mostly Rcpp-armadillo implementations, offering computationally efficient Bayesian geostatistical modeling."
